N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 328.12 - Filing of notices

State Regulations

All notices required to be filed with the chairman pursuant
to this Part, shall be deemed filed when received by the chairman, Workers'
Compensation Board, 180 Livingston Street, Brooklyn, NY
11248. Notes
